001820 REM ---------------------------------------------------------
001830 L10: ! Kundestamm lesen
001840      KY10$ = "1"&FKDNR$
001850      FL% = 10 \ READ #10,KY10$:K8%,K9%,KF%,KNR,KA1$,KA2$,KST$,KPL,KOR$,KL$,KSW$,KI$,KUG%,KDB,K1%,K2%,KRB%,KFA%,KTU%,KGR%,KBK%,KAN%,KMG%,KBZ%,KLB$,K3%,KPO%,KOP%,KT$,K4%,K5%,TEMP$,TEMP$,FK1% \ CLEAR FL%
